#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Modern Weapon Pack Expanded"
msgstr "现代武器包扩展版"

#. ~ Description for Modern Weapon Pack Expanded
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"This mod adds more real world firearms to the game. It was derived from "
"Modern Weapons Pack by crom. It also overrides most of core game guns to use"
" more calibers. INCLUDES PATCH OPTION in modern_extras folder to disable "
"overriding of core game guns."
msgstr ""
"此模组为游戏添加了更多现实世界的枪械。它衍生自crom的现代武器包。同时覆盖了大部分核心游戏枪械以使用更多口径。包含在modern_extras文件夹中的补丁选项可禁用对核心游戏枪械的覆盖。"

#: .\modern_ammo\modern_ammo.json
msgid ".30-30 Winchester"
msgid_plural ".30-30 Winchester"
msgstr[0] ".30-30温彻斯特"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.30-30 Winchester', 'str_pl': '.30-30
#. Winchester'}
#: .\modern_ammo\modern_ammo.json
msgid ""
"At short-range, with considerably lower recoil than a .3006, the .30-30 "
"Winchester is very popular with hunters of deer, black bear, and even moose."
"  Its 150gr round-nose cartridge is well suited for the tubular magazines of"
" lever-action rifles."
msgstr ".30-30温彻斯特在短距离内后坐力远低于.3006，深受猎鹿、黑熊甚至驼鹿的猎人喜爱。其150格令圆头弹非常适合杠杆式步枪的管状弹仓。"

#: .\modern_ammo\modern_ammo.json
msgid "reloaded .30-30 Winchester"
msgid_plural "reloaded .30-30 Winchester"
msgstr[0] "重装.30-30温彻斯特"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reloaded .30-30 Winchester', 'str_pl': 'reloaded
#. .30-30 Winchester'}
#: .\modern_ammo\modern_ammo.json
msgid ""
"At short-range, with considerably lower recoil than a .3006, the .30-30 "
"Winchester is very popular with hunters of deer, black bear, and even moose."
"  Its 150gr round-nose cartridge is well suited for the tubular magazines of"
" lever-action rifles.  This one has been hand-reloaded."
msgstr ""
".30-30温彻斯特在短距离内后坐力远低于.3006，深受猎鹿、黑熊甚至驼鹿的猎人喜爱。其150格令圆头弹非常适合杠杆式步枪的管状弹仓。此发为手工重装弹。"

#: .\modern_ammo\modern_ammo.json
msgid ".357 Magnum"
msgid_plural ".357 Magnum"
msgstr[0] ".357马格南"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.357 Magnum', 'str_pl': '.357 Magnum'}
#: .\modern_ammo\modern_ammo.json
msgid ""
"The high velocity and high energy .357 Magnum, with 158gr JHP in an "
"elongated .38 Special cartridge, was developed in the 1930s.  Renowned for "
"its stopping power, the .357 is easily capable of bringing down medium to "
"large game."
msgstr ""
"高速高能量的.357马格南弹，采用加长的.38特种弹壳配158格令空尖弹，于1930年代开发。以其制止力闻名，.357能轻松放倒中型至大型猎物。"

#: .\modern_ammo\modern_ammo.json
msgid "reloaded .357 Magnum"
msgid_plural "reloaded .357 Magnum"
msgstr[0] "重装.357马格南"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reloaded .357 Magnum', 'str_pl': 'reloaded .357
#. Magnum'}
#: .\modern_ammo\modern_ammo.json
msgid ""
"The high velocity and high energy .357 Magnum, with 125gr JHP in an "
"elongated .38 Special cartridge, was developed in the 1930s.  Renowned for "
"its stopping power, the .357 is easily capable of bringing down medium to "
"large game.  This one has been hand-reloaded."
msgstr ""
"高速高能量的.357马格南弹，采用加长的.38特种弹壳配125格令空尖弹，于1930年代开发。以其制止力闻名，.357能轻松放倒中型至大型猎物。此发为手工重装弹。"

