#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"A brushed stainless steel .45 patterned after the Colt M1911 with a seven "
"inch barrel."
msgstr "一款基于柯尔特M1911设计的拉丝不锈钢.45手枪，配备七英寸枪管。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "APB Stechkin"
msgid_plural "APB Stechkins"
msgstr[0] "APB斯捷奇金"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The Russian, APB Stechkin, or Avtomaticheskij Pistolet Besshumnyj, is a Cold"
" War era, double action, automatic machine pistol used by Spetsnaz special "
"forces."
msgstr ""
"俄罗斯APB斯捷奇金，或称Avtomaticheskij Pistolet Besshumnyj，是一款冷战时期的双动自动冲锋手枪，由特种部队使用。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
#: .\modern_smg\modern_smg.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Strike One"
msgid_plural "Strike Ones"
msgstr[0] "一击"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"Of Italian design, the Arsenal Firearms Strike One is a short recoil "
"operated, hammerless striker-fired, semi-automatic pistol."
msgstr "意大利设计的阿森纳火器一击是一款短后坐力操作、无击锤击针击发半自动手枪。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "AutoMag"
msgid_plural "AutoMags"
msgstr[0] "自动马格南"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The AutoMag is easily recognizable because of a distinctive vented rib along"
" its barrel.  It has a recoil operated, locking rotary bolt similar to many "
"rifles, and is a highly regarded semi-automatic pistol."
msgstr "自动马格南因其枪管上独特的通风肋条而易于识别。它采用后坐力操作、旋转闭锁枪机，类似于许多步枪，是一款备受推崇的半自动手枪。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Beretta 93R"
msgid_plural "Beretta 93Rs"
msgstr[0] "伯莱塔93R"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The Beretta 93 Raffica machine pistol used by Italian counter-terrorism "
"police and military forces."
msgstr "伯莱塔93 Raffica冲锋手枪，由意大利反恐警察和军事部队使用。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Browning HP"
msgid_plural "Browning HPs"
msgstr[0] "勃朗宁HP"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The Browning Hi Power, introduced in 1935, has been a widely used military "
"service sidearm for many countries.  It is a single action, recoil operated "
"pistol."
msgstr "勃朗宁大威力手枪于1935年推出，已成为许多国家广泛使用的军用制式手枪。它是一款单动、后坐力操作手枪。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Colt USMC M45A1 CQBP"
msgid_plural "Colt USMC M45A1 CQBPs"
msgstr[0] "柯尔特美国海军陆战队M45A1 CQBP"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The US Marine Corp standard-issue side arm, this single action, recoil "
"operated, semi-automatic Close Quarter Battle Pistol is a M1911-style "
"handgun with a sand-tan finish."
msgstr "美国海军陆战队标准配发手枪，这款单动、后坐力操作半自动近战手枪是一款M1911风格手枪，采用沙褐色涂装。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Coonan .357 Magnum Automatic"
msgid_plural "Coonan .357 Magnum Automatics"
msgstr[0] "库南.357马格南自动手枪"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The Coonan Compensated .357 Magnum is a recoil operated, m1911-style "
"automatic pistol of high quality."
msgstr "库南补偿型.357马格南是一款后坐力操作、M1911风格的高品质自动手枪。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "H&K 45T"
msgid_plural "H&K 45Ts"
msgstr[0] "H&K 45T"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The Heckler & Koch 45 Tactical was intended to replace the Berreta M9 as the"
" standard US Military service weapon in the Joint Combat Pistol program "
"which was suspended due to budgetary contraints.  It is a double-action "
"pistol, short-recoil operated, using modified Browning-type locking system "
"and tilting barrel."
msgstr ""
"Heckler & Koch "
"45战术型手枪原计划在联合战斗手枪项目中取代伯莱塔M9，成为美军标准制式武器，后因预算限制而搁置。它是一款双动手枪，采用短后坐力操作，改良版勃朗宁式闭锁系统与倾斜枪管设计。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "H&K 45CT"
msgid_plural "H&K 45CTs"
msgstr[0] "H&K 45CT"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The Heckler & Koch 45 Compact Tactical is a double-action pistol, short-"
"recoil operated, using modified Browning-type locking system and tilting "
"barrel."
msgstr "Heckler & Koch 45紧凑战术型是一款双动手枪，采用短后坐力操作，改良版勃朗宁式闭锁系统与倾斜枪管设计。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Mare's Leg"
msgid_plural "Mare's Legs"
msgstr[0] "母马腿"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The Henry Lever Action Mare's Leg has an octogon barrel with brass barrel "
"bands and a brass receiver plate.  Classified as a pistol in the US, this is"
" a cut-down version of a full sized rifle."
msgstr "亨利杠杆式母马腿步枪配备八边形枪管、黄铜枪管箍和黄铜机匣板。在美国被归类为手枪，这是全尺寸步枪的截短版本。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "High Standard Semi-Automatic"
msgid_plural "High Standard Semi-Automatics"
msgstr[0] "海标准半自动手枪"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "A US Military, WWII era, target pistol for competition."
msgstr "一款美军二战时期的竞赛用靶枪。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "High Standard HDM"
msgid_plural "High Standard HDMs"
msgstr[0] "海标准HDM"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"An OSS, US Special Operations Forces, and CIA pistol common between "
"1942-1951.  It is still found, today, in United States inventories."
msgstr "一款在1942年至1951年间常见的OSS（美国战略服务局）、美国特种部队和CIA手枪。至今仍可在美国库存中找到。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "High Standard Deluxe"
msgid_plural "High Standard Deluxes"
msgstr[0] "海标准豪华型"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"A common 9mm revolver loved for its dependability and comfortable grip."
msgstr "一款常见的9毫米左轮手枪，以其可靠性和舒适握把而备受喜爱。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Kahr K9"
msgid_plural "Kahr K9s"
msgstr[0] "Kahr K9"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"A popular concealed carry option for law enforcement officers, the Kahr K9 "
"is a double action only, compact semi-automatic of solid steel construction "
"with polymer grips."
msgstr "Kahr K9是执法人员常用的隐蔽携带选择，它是一款纯双动、紧凑型半自动手枪，采用全钢结构与聚合物握把。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Korth Nibelungen"
msgid_plural "Korth Nibelungens"
msgstr[0] "Korth Nibelungen"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"Made with cold forged Damascus steel, the Korth Nibelungen is at the "
"pinnacle of German precision engineering."
msgstr "采用冷锻大马士革钢制成，Korth Nibelungen代表了德国精密工程的巅峰。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Korth Combat"
msgid_plural "Korth Combats"
msgstr[0] "Korth Combat"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"This wheelgun is hand crafted with German precision engineering.  The Korth "
"Combat is a double action work of art machined from the finest billet steel."
msgstr "这款左轮手枪采用德国精密工程手工打造。Korth Combat是一款双动艺术品，由最优质的钢坯加工而成。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Manurhin MR 73"
msgid_plural "Manurhin MR 73s"
msgstr[0] "Manurhin MR 73"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"A double-action revolver from France, the Manurhin MR 73 was a standard "
"issue firearm for the French Police Nationale and Gendarmerie Nationale.  "
"Its performance, durability, and accuracy have reached a legendary status."
msgstr "Manurhin MR 73是一款法国产双动左轮手枪，曾是法国国家警察和国家宪兵队的标准配枪。其性能、耐用性和精准度已达到传奇地位。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Rohrbaugh R9s"
msgid_plural "Rohrbaugh R9ss"
msgstr[0] "Rohrbaugh R9s"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The Rohrbaugh R9s is a hammerless, compact semi-automatic.  Lightweight, "
"double action, it is operated with a short recoil and a locking breech."
msgstr "Rohrbaugh R9s是一款无击锤紧凑型半自动手枪。轻量双动设计，采用短后坐力与闭锁枪机操作。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "S&W 59"
msgid_plural "S&W 59s"
msgstr[0] "S&W 59"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "The Smith & Wesson Model 59 double-action, semi-automatic pistol."
msgstr "史密斯&韦森59型双动半自动手枪。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "S&W 686"
msgid_plural "S&W 686s"
msgstr[0] "S&W 686"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"The stainless steel Smith & Wesson Model 686 double-action revolver is a "
"popular sidearm among several US law enforcement agencies and police."
msgstr "不锈钢史密斯&韦森686型双动左轮手枪是美国多个执法机构和警察部门常用的副武器。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid "Vörös-Danuvia VD-01"
msgid_plural "Vörös-Danuvia VD-01s"
msgstr[0] "Vörös-Danuvia VD-01"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun.json
msgid ""
"A Hungarian weapon, the Vörös-Danuvia Machine-Pistol VD-01 features a "
"distinctive under-barrel cylindrical magazine forward the trigger guard."
msgstr "Vörös-Danuvia VD-01是一款匈牙利武器，其特色是枪管下方、扳机护圈前方设有独特的圆柱形弹匣。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid ".22 magazine"
msgid_plural ".22 magazines"
msgstr[0] ".22弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.22 magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "A standard 10 round capacity magazine for a .22 pistol."
msgstr ".22手枪的标准10发容量弹匣。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid ".357 magazine"
msgid_plural ".357 magazines"
msgstr[0] ".357弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.357 magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "The standard magazine for a .357 semi-automatic, holds 7 rounds."
msgstr ".357半自动手枪的标准弹匣，可容纳7发子弹。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "Strike One 9mm magazine"
msgid_plural "Strike One 9mm magazines"
msgstr[0] "Strike One 9毫米弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Strike One 9mm magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "The standard magazine for the Browning HP, holds 17 rounds staggered."
msgstr "勃朗宁HP的标准弹匣，采用交错排列，可容纳17发子弹。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "S&W 9mm magazine"
msgid_plural "S&W 9mm magazines"
msgstr[0] "S&W 9毫米弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'S&W 9mm magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "The S&W 9mm magazine, holds 14 rounds double column."
msgstr "S&W 9毫米弹匣，采用双排设计，可容纳14发子弹。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "Browning HP 9mm magazine"
msgid_plural "Browning HP 9mm magazines"
msgstr[0] "勃朗宁HP 9毫米弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Browning HP 9mm magazine'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Strike One .40 magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_obsolete.json
msgid "The standard magazine for the Browning HP, holds 13 rounds staggered."
msgstr "勃朗宁HP的标准弹匣，采用交错排列，可容纳13发子弹。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "compact concealed carry 9mm magazine"
msgid_plural "compact concealed carry 9mm magazines"
msgstr[0] "紧凑型隐蔽携带9毫米弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'compact concealed carry 9mm magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "The standard magazine for a compact handgun, holds 7 rounds."
msgstr "紧凑型手枪的标准弹匣，可容纳7发子弹。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "Stechkin magazine"
msgid_plural "Stechkin magazines"
msgstr[0] "斯捷奇金弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stechkin magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid ""
"The standard magazine for the APB Stechkin, holds 20 rounds double-stacked "
"with a double feed."
msgstr "APB斯捷奇金的标准弹匣，采用双排双进设计，可容纳20发子弹。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid "VD-01 cylindrical magazine"
msgid_plural "VD-01 cylindrical magazines"
msgstr[0] "VD-01圆柱形弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'VD-01 cylindrical magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_magazines.json
msgid ""
"An under-barrel, 33-round, helical loading, cylindrical magazine made for "
"the Voros-Danuvia VD-01."
msgstr "专为Voros-Danuvia VD-01设计的枪管下挂式33发螺旋供弹圆柱形弹匣。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_obsolete.json
msgid "Strike One .40 magazine"
msgid_plural "Strike One .40 magazines"
msgstr[0] "Strike One .40口径弹匣"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_obsolete.json
msgid "Browning HP .40 magazine"
msgid_plural "Browning HP .40 magazines"
msgstr[0] "勃朗宁HP .40口径弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Browning HP .40 magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_obsolete.json
msgid ""
"The .40 magazine for the Browning HP, holds 10 rounds double-stacked with a "
"staggered feed."
msgstr "勃朗宁HP的.40口径弹匣，采用双排交错供弹设计，可容纳10发子弹。"

#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_obsolete.json
msgid "compact concealed carry .40 magazine"
msgid_plural "compact concealed carry .40 magazines"
msgstr[0] "紧凑型隐蔽携带.40口径弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'compact concealed carry .40 magazine'}
#: .\modern_handgun\modern_handgun_obsolete.json
msgid "The standard magazine for a compact handgun, holds 6 rounds."
msgstr "紧凑型手枪的标准弹匣，可容纳6发子弹。"

#: .\modern_launcher\modern_launcher.json
msgid "GL06 stand alone launcher"
msgid_plural "GL06 stand alone launchers"
msgstr[0] "GL06独立发射器"

#: .\modern_launcher\modern_launcher.json
msgid ""
"The Brügger & Thomet GL06 grenade launcher is one of the most accurate "
"launchers available.  It features vertical loading with a folding buttstock "
"and detachable forward grip."
msgstr "Brügger & Thomet GL06榴弹发射器是现有最精确的发射器之一。它采用垂直装填方式，配备折叠枪托和可拆卸前握把。"

#: .\modern_launcher\modern_launcher.json
msgid "RGM-40 Kastet"
msgid_plural "RGM-40 Kastets"
msgstr[0] "RGM-40 Kastet"

#: .\modern_launcher\modern_launcher.json
msgid ""
"The RGM-40 Kastet light grenade launcher is intended to be used by law "
"enforcement agencies for anti-riot control but can also be used to engage "
"other targets.  It is muzzle-loaded, has a self-cocking trigger mechanism, "
"an AK style pistol grip, and extendable buttstock."
msgstr ""
"RGM-40 "
"Kastet轻型榴弹发射器旨在供执法机构用于防暴控制，但也可用于攻击其他目标。它采用前装式设计，配备自击发扳机机构、AK式手枪握把和可伸缩枪托。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "AR57 LEM"
msgid_plural "AR57 LEMs"
msgstr[0] "AR57 LEM"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"This short barrel rifle (6in Fluted Barrel) is a familiar AR style personal "
"defense weapon.  It fires 5.7x28mm ammunition and takes a FN P90 magazine.  "
"This one is a semi automatic Law Enforcement Model."
msgstr "这款短管步枪（6英寸凹槽枪管）是常见的AR式个人防卫武器。它发射5.7x28毫米弹药，使用FN P90弹匣。此型号为半自动执法模型。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "R93 Tactical 2"
msgid_plural "R93 Tactical 2s"
msgstr[0] "R93 Tactical 2"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"The Blaser R93 Tactical 2 is a straight pull, bolt action sniper rifle. "
msgstr "Blaser R93 Tactical 2是一款直拉式栓动狙击步枪。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "CETME Ameli"
msgid_plural "CETME Amelis"
msgstr[0] "CETME Ameli"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"The CETME Ameli light machine gun used by the Spanish military resembles the"
" German MG3 but uses a roller delayed blowback action to reduce recoil as "
"the bolt body travels back on the bolt spring."
msgstr "西班牙军队使用的CETME Ameli轻机枪与德国MG3相似，但采用滚柱延迟后坐式设计，通过枪机在复进簧上后移来减少后坐力。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "Chiappa M1-9"
msgid_plural "Chiappa M1-9s"
msgstr[0] "Chiappa M1-9"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"A replica of the standard M1 Carbine of WWII, the Italian semi-automatic, "
"the Chiappa M1-9, is a blowback operated plinker and small game hunting "
"rifle."
msgstr "作为二战标准M1卡宾枪的复制品，意大利半自动Chiappa M1-9是一款采用后坐式操作的娱乐射击和小型猎物狩猎步枪。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "Desert Tech MDR"
msgid_plural "Desert Tech MDRs"
msgstr[0] "沙漠科技MDR"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"With a bullpup design, the Desert Tech Micro Dynamic Rifle is a gas "
"operated, ambidextrous assault rifle."
msgstr "采用无托式设计的沙漠科技微型动态步枪是一款气动操作、左右手通用的突击步枪。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "Enfield L85A2"
msgid_plural "Enfield L85A2s"
msgstr[0] "恩菲尔德L85A2"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"A bullpup assault rifle, the standard issue service rifle of the British "
"Armed Forces, the Enfield L85A2, uses a short-stroke gas piston system and a"
" rotating bolt."
msgstr "恩菲尔德L85A2是一款无托式突击步枪，作为英国武装部队的标准制式步枪，采用短行程气动活塞系统和旋转式枪机。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "FAD assault rifle"
msgid_plural "FAD assault rifles"
msgstr[0] "FAD突击步枪"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"From Peru, the FAD assault rifle, (or Fusil Automático Doble,) is a compact "
"infantry support weapon used by vehicle crews as back-up weapon.  It "
"features a bullpup design with an integrated grenade launcher."
msgstr ""
"来自秘鲁的FAD突击步枪（或称Fusil Automático "
"Doble）是一款紧凑型步兵支援武器，被车辆乘员用作备用武器。它采用无托式设计并集成了榴弹发射器。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "FX-05 Xiuhcoatl"
msgid_plural "FX-05 Xiuhcoatls"
msgstr[0] "FX-05 火蛇"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"The Fire Serpent, a modern assault rifle of the Mexican Armed Forces, "
"Fuerzas Armadas de Mexico.  Closely patterned after the German made HK G36."
msgstr "火蛇步枪是墨西哥武装部队（Fuerzas Armadas de Mexico）的一款现代突击步枪，其设计紧密仿照德国制造的HK G36。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "Henry Lever Action"
msgid_plural "Henry Lever Actions"
msgstr[0] "亨利杠杆式步枪"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"The Henry Lever Action has an octogon barrel with brass barrel bands and a "
"brass receiver plate.  This beloved repeater has a home with many a hunter "
"of venison."
msgstr "亨利杠杆式步枪配备八角形枪管、黄铜枪管箍和黄铜机匣板。这款备受喜爱的连发步枪是许多猎鹿人的心头好。"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid "Galil assault rifle"
msgid_plural "Galil assault rifles"
msgstr[0] "加利尔突击步枪"

#: .\modern_rifle\modern_rifle.json
msgid ""
"Built by Israel Military Industries, the Galil is a gas operated/rotating "
"bolt assault rifle whose design was greatly influenced by the Valmet Rk.62 "
"and the AK-47.  It features an aluminum side folding stock and a diopter "
"sight."
msgstr ""
